+++ build/instdso.sh    Wed Jun 16 11:43:31 2004
@@ -61,7 +61,7 @@
 fi
 
 DLNAME=`grep "^dlname" $TARGETDIR/$DSOARCHIVE_BASENAME | sed -e
"s/dlname='\([^']*\)'/\1/"`
-LIBRARY_NAMES=`grep "library_names" $TARGETDIR/$DSOARCHIVE_BASENAME | sed -e
"s/dlname='\([^']*\)'/\1/"`
+LIBRARY_NAMES=`grep "library_names" $TARGETDIR/$DSOARCHIVE_BASENAME | sed -e
"s/library_names='\([^']*\)'/\1/"`
 LIBRARY_NAMES=`echo $LIBRARY_NAMES | sed -e "s/ *$DLNAME//g"`
 
 if test -z "$DLNAME"
